. I have a growing passion for cybersecurity and am actively involved in learning about digital safety, vulnerability assessment, and system protection.",[1151,1349],"Hello! I&lsquo;m Osan Shrestha from Kathmandu, Nepal. I have a growing passion for cybersecurity and am actively involved in learning about digital safety, vulnerability assessment, and system protection.",[1151,1349],"Hello! I&#39;m Osan Shrestha from Kathmandu, Nepal. I have a growing passion for cybersecurity and am actively involved in learning about digital safety, vulnerability assessment, and system protection.",[1151,1349],"Hello! I&rsquo;m Osan Shrestha from Kathmandu, Nepal. I have a growing passion for cybersecurity and am actively involved in learning about digital safety, vulnerability assessment, and system protection.",[15,45],[1418,1771],"\n                I&apos;m a dedicated cybersecurity enthusiast from Kathmandu, Nepal, currently pursuing my education while actively engaging in cybersecurity research and challenges. With a strong foundation in science and mathematics, I've developed a keen interest in information security, vulnerability assessment, and penetration testing.\n              ",[1418,1771],"\n                I&lsquo;m a dedicated cybersecurity enthusiast from Kathmandu, Nepal, currently pursuing my education while actively engaging in cybersecurity research and challenges. With a strong foundation in science and mathematics, I've developed a keen interest in information security, vulnerability assessment, and penetration testing.\n              ",[1418,1771],"\n                I&#39;m a dedicated cybersecurity enthusiast from Kathmandu, Nepal, currently pursuing my education while actively engaging in cybersecurity research and challenges. With a strong foundation in science and mathematics, I've developed a keen interest in information security, vulnerability assessment, and penetration testing.\n              ",[1418,1771],"\n                I&rsquo;m a dedicated cyber